```', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 8, 23, 22, 6, 19, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'clayjohn', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 953147893, 'comment_body': "This shouldn't be called if ``inst->data->lightmap_size_global_uniform_pos`` is invalid
