					}
```", 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 8, 23, 22, 7, 3, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'clayjohn', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 956775814, 'comment_body': 'Our style guide on code comments is to start with a capital and end with a period', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 8, 28, 20, 9, 54, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'clayjohn', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 956776163, 'comment_body': 'Same comment as for GLES3', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 8, 28, 20, 12, 38, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'clayjohn', 'type': 'User'}, {'comment_id': 956787479, 'comment_body': 'Done.', 'comment_created': datetime.datetime(2022, 8, 28, 22, 5, 24, tzinfo=datetime.timezone.utc), 'commenter': 'techiepriyansh', 'type': 'User'}]

